🧮 Soft Calc — Glassmorphism Calculator

Soft Calc is a modern and responsive calculator web application built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.
It features a beautiful glassmorphism UI, smooth animations, keyboard support, and real-time arithmetic calculations.

✨ Features
* Modern Glassmorphism Design
* Responsive User Interface
* Addition, Subtraction, Multiplication & Division
* Percentage Calculation
* Positive/Negative Toggle (±)
* Backspace Functionality
* Keyboard Support
* Real-Time Expression Display
* Animated Buttons & Floating Background Blobs
* Error Handling for Invalid Operations
* Smooth Hover & Click Effects

🛠️ Technologies Used
HTML5
CSS3
JavaScript

🎨 UI Highlights
Soft pastel gradient background
Floating animated blobs
Frosted glass calculator panel
Smooth transitions and hover effects
Fully responsive button grid
Elegant typography using Google Fonts

📁 Project Structure
Soft-Calc/
│── index.html

▶️ How to Run the Project
Download or clone the repository.
Open the project folder.
Run the index.html file in any web browser.

